     \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#martaf\">\n                \u003Cp>This epitaph, already recognised as Christian by Kirchhoff, has a formula fairly attested in Catania without the expression \u003Cforeign xml:lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται\u003C/foreign> and with only the name of the deceased followed by the date of death (expressed with the aorist of \u003Cforeign xml:lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω\u003C/foreign>) and occasionally the age (but not in this case): e.g. IG 14.551 = \u003Cref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001370\">ISic001370\u003C/ref>.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Amico\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1741\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>276\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F5INCW3T\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Castelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1769\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>263 no.10\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SPTB56H3\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Castelli\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1784\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>281 no.10\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/7PSFHSUH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrara\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1829\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>392 no.8\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/82T4IWDN\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Kaibel\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1890\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">565\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>215\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Kirchhoff\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1877\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>9511\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/533T8HNS\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
